=== Cultural properties ===
[[File:Ohbejinja02.jpg|150px|thumb|Great camphor tree (Hyogo Prefecture designated natural monument)]]
* Great camphor tree, designated {{ill|lt=natural monument|Q23790|WD=Q23790|1=Natural monument}} by {{ill|lt=Hyōgo Prefecture|Q130290|WD=Q130290|1=Hyōgo Prefecture}} (designated March 22, Shōwa 41) - root circumference approx. 12 {{ill|lt=meters|Q11573|WD=Q11573|1=Metre}}, height approx. 30 m, estimated age 500 years.

=== Transportation ===
* About 8 minutes on foot from {{ill|lt=Kawanishi-Noseguchi Station|Q3969857|WD=Q3969857|1=Kawanishi-Noseguchi Station}} on the {{ill|lt=Hankyu Takarazuka Main Line|Q3832859|WD=Q3832859|1=Hankyu Takarazuka Main Line}}

